🍝 I made this veggie-loaded pasta to satisfy my cravings and it was so SO satisfying.

🥦🌽 You can literally throw in any veggies you love I added cherry tomatoes (for tanginess 😉), normal tomatoes, onions, red and green bell peppers trust me, it was colorful and full of fiber.

Had added around 40-50 gms of paneer to the gravy. And then grinded up everything!

🧄 A little garlic, olive oil, chili flakes, and herbs to keep it flavorful… then in goes the boiled pasta and that soft paneer for the protein kick.

😮‍💨 It was hitting the spot! Like, all my cravings? Gone. Satiety? Through the roof.

✨So if you’re looking for a high-protein, fiber-rich pasta that feels like comfort food but fuels your body please save this recipe. You’re gonna love it.
